Package: InFieldR
Type: Package
Title: Regression Model of in-situ data with raster data
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Charl & Arthur
Maintainer: The package maintainer <arthur.dreher@stud-mail.uni-wuerzburg.de>
Description: More about what it does (maybe more than one line)
    Our packages helps to first suggest with a regression model how many in-situ values should be taken to receive a sufficient output and afterwards it uses those collected values to predict values for a whole map (depended on the input-scene.
